{"id":"api/common/TitleCasePipe","title":"TitleCasePipe","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/TitleCasePipe\", \"name\": \"TitleCasePipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/case_conversion_pipes.ts#L59-L99\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"titlecasepipe\">TitleCasePipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe#titlecasepipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"evwl461d95dgcrsh1u8ekj42n\">把文字轉換成標題形式。\n把每個單詞的第一個字母轉成大寫形式，並把單詞的其餘部分轉成小寫形式。\n單詞之間用任意空白字元進行分隔，比如空格、Tab 或換行符。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n<section class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\"><a href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">titlecase</a></span> }}</code-example>\n\n  \n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code>CommonModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">輸入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6y18uxg2a2xx1qj04ok4glp0s\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/LowerCasePipe\"><code>LowerCasePipe</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/UpperCasePipe\"><code>UpperCasePipe</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/TitleCasePipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7q6eg915smdw25srqqpq9n6wm\">下面的例子示範瞭如何把多種字串轉成標題形式。</p>\n<code-example path=\"common/pipes/ts/titlecase_pipe.ts\" region=\"TitleCasePipe\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'titlecase-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ 'some string' | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"Some String\" --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ 'tHIs is mIXeD CaSe' | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"This Is Mixed Case\" --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ \"it's non-trivial question\" | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"It's Non-trivial Question\" --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ 'one,two,three' | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"One,two,three\" --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ 'true|false' | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"True|false\" --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;{{ 'foo-vs-bar' | titlecase }}&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- output is expected to be \"Foo-vs-bar\" --&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`,\n})\nexport class TitleCasePipeComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/LowerCasePipe\n - api/common/UpperCasePipe\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/testing-pipes\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/LowerCasePipe\n - api/common/TitleCasePipe#input-value\n - api/common/TitleCasePipe#see-also\n - api/common/TitleCasePipe#titlecasepipe\n - api/common/TitleCasePipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/TitleCasePipe#匯出自\n - api/common/UpperCasePipe\n - api/core/Component\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/case_conversion_pipes.ts#L59-L99\n-->"}